name: Ghoul School
description:
This Photoshop collage project took a REALLY long time for 8 year old artist Big 8 Art to do, he he was determined to make some great art for the #HENHalloween.  He hopes to use any money he makes from his Halloween projects to buy Christmas presents for his mom, dad, sister and brother.

Big 8 Art says, Thank you so much for looking at my art!
